title: Avalanche (AVAX) Overtakes Dogecoin (DOGE) as Ninth-Largest Crypto by Market Cap
description: The Avalanche (AVAX) network has been outperforming the leading meme-inspired cryptocurrency by market capitalization Dogecoin (DOGE), to the point it has now become the ninth largest digital asset by the metric, with a $14.1 billion market cap.
